T4_MOUNT_GIANTSTAG.name: Adept's Giant Stag
T4_MOUNT_GIANTSTAG.desc: Stags are fast and strong, making them favored mounts of gatherers and couriers.

T6_MOUNT_GIANTSTAG_MOOSE.name: Moose
T6_MOUNT_GIANTSTAG_MOOSE.desc: Moose are fast and strong, making them favored mounts of gatherers and couriers.

T6_MOUNT_DIREWOLF.name: Direwolf
T6_MOUNT_DIREWOLF.desc: One of Albion's fastest mounts, the Direwolf specializes in hunting, pursuit, and evasion.

T8_MOUNT_MAMMOTH_TRANSPORT.name: Elder's Transport Mammoth
T8_MOUNT_MAMMOTH_TRANSPORT.desc: What a mammoth lacks in speed, it makes up for in enormous carrying capacity. Mammoths are the favored transport of anyone wishing to move really, really large quantities of goods.

T5_MOUNT_MOABIRD_FW_BRIDGEWATCH.desc: Mount - A special breed originally from the steppe around Bridgewatch.

T6_MOUNT_SIEGE_BALLISTA.name: Siege Ballista
T6_MOUNT_SIEGE_BALLISTA.desc: Battle Mount - Immune to displacement effects.

T8_MOUNT_HORSE_UNDEAD@1.name: Spectral Bonehorse
T8_MOUNT_HORSE_UNDEAD@1.desc: Secret rituals allow the spirit of an ancient knight's mount to animate the cooling corpse of a sacrificial horse. Loyal and obedient, its appearance nevertheless strikes fear into its foes.

T5_MOUNT_COUGAR_KEEPER@1.name: Swiftclaw
T5_MOUNT_COUGAR_KEEPER@1.desc: Keeper scouts have used these fast animals to scout the wilds and will never surrender a cub willingly.

T8_MOUNT_COUGAR_KEEPER@1.name: Rageclaw
T8_MOUNT_COUGAR_KEEPER@1.desc: The fastest and most aggressive Swiftclaw cubs are raised as Rageclaws: battle mounts for berserker cavalry. Raised from birth to tolerate the fury of battle, Rageclaws deliver their riders right into the heart of the enemy ranks.

T8_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_MORGANA@1.name: Morgana Nightmare
T8_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_MORGANA@1.desc: Every Morgana horse-breeder dreams of birthing a foal angry and aggressive enough to survive demonic possession. The resulting creature is almost as dangerous to its rider as it is to its enemies.

T8_MOUNT_RABBIT_EASTER.name: Spring Cottontail
T8_MOUNT_RABBIT_EASTER.desc: Spring Cottontails are only found during the Rites of Spring. They're very fast companions, but can grow extremely irritable without a strict diet of chocolate.

T8_MOUNT_RABBIT_EASTER_DARK@1.name: Caerleon Cottontail
T8_MOUNT_RABBIT_EASTER_DARK@1.desc: The Dreaded Rabbit of Caerbann...Caerba...Caerleon. You were warned to only feed it chocolate, but did you listen? Oh, it's just a harmless little bunny, isn't it?

UNIQUE_MOUNT_RAM_XMAS.name: Yule Ram
UNIQUE_MOUNT_RAM_XMAS.desc: Mount - With this mount you can celebrate the Midwinter Festival

T7_MOUNT_SWAMPDRAGON_AVALON_BASILISK.name: Avalonian Basilisk
T7_MOUNT_SWAMPDRAGON_AVALON_BASILISK.desc: A Swamp Dragon infused with Avalonian Energy. Can discharge energy to escape from attackers.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_BAT_TELLAFRIEND.name: Recruiter's Saddled Bat
UNIQUE_MOUNT_BAT_TELLAFRIEND.desc: Referral Mount - Can fly on its own, though with a human on top it becomes too heavy to fly over obstacles.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_GIANTTOAD_02_TELLAFRIEND.name: Recruiter's Giant Frog
UNIQUE_MOUNT_GIANTTOAD_02_TELLAFRIEND.desc: Mount - Her name is Berta. Born in a backwater swamp, she dreams of someday seeing the world.

T5_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_SKIN_01.name: Expert's Warhorse
T5_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_SKIN_01.desc: An armored horse bearing the impressive banner of its rider's guild. Ideal for raising morale in big battles.

T6_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_SKIN_01.name: Master's Warhorse
T6_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_SKIN_01.desc: An armored horse bearing the impressive banner of its rider's guild. Ideal for raising morale in big battles.

T7_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_SKIN_01.name: Grandmaster's Warhorse
T7_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_SKIN_01.desc: An armored horse bearing the impressive banner of its rider's guild. Ideal for raising morale in big battles.

T8_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_SKIN_01.name: Elder's Warhorse
T8_MOUNT_ARMORED_HORSE_SKIN_01.desc: An armored horse bearing the impressive banner of its rider's guild. Ideal for raising morale in big battles.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_BAT_PERSONAL.name: Spectral Bat
UNIQUE_MOUNT_BAT_PERSONAL.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - Fast and ethereal, with formidable speed and the ability to teleport over short distances.

T7_MOUNT_MONITORLIZARD_ADC.name: Pest Lizard
T7_MOUNT_MONITORLIZARD_ADC.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - Quick and hard to catch, this baleful creature can emit intoxicating poison when threatened.

T7_MOUNT_HUSKY_ADC.name: Snow Husky
T7_MOUNT_HUSKY_ADC.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - A very good sprinter with a positive and loyal attitude towards humans.

T6_MOUNT_FROSTRAM_ADC.name: Frost Ram
T6_MOUNT_FROSTRAM_ADC.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - This mount's skillful leap makes it hard to catch.

T7_MOUNT_TERRORBIRD_ADC.name: Saddled Terrorbird
T7_MOUNT_TERRORBIRD_ADC.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - These animals like to toy with humans, but once trained become very fast and reliable companions.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_BEAR_KEEPER_ADC.name: Grizzly Bear
UNIQUE_MOUNT_BEAR_KEEPER_ADC.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - A strong animal that can easily carry a lot of weight. Its mighty presence alone strikes fear in any attackers.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_BLACK_PANTHER_ADC.name: Black Panther
UNIQUE_MOUNT_BLACK_PANTHER_ADC.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - A real hunter, very swift with the ability to temporarily sprint at high speed to catch any prey.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_MORGANA_RAVEN_ADC.name: Morgana Raven
UNIQUE_MOUNT_MORGANA_RAVEN_ADC.desc: The disciples of Morgana seem to worship this fascinating animal and will likely consider riding it to be heresy.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_GIANT_HORSE_ADC.name: Gallant Horse
UNIQUE_MOUNT_GIANT_HORSE_ADC.desc: A heavy horse, also known as Cold Blood. Fearless and not easily impressed by any unforeseen threats.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_UNDEAD_DIREBOAR_ADC.name: Spectral Direboar
UNIQUE_MOUNT_UNDEAD_DIREBOAR_ADC.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - Neither burden nor death can stop this beast, which walks in two worlds at once.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_DIVINE_OWL_ADC.name: Divine Owl
UNIQUE_MOUNT_DIVINE_OWL_ADC.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - A being bestowed with divine wisdom and the gift of clairvoyance.

UNIQUE_MOUNT_HERETIC_MULE_ADC.name: Heretic Combat Mule
UNIQUE_MOUNT_HERETIC_MULE_ADC.desc: Adventurer's Challenge Reward - An abomination of war that could only have been contrived by the most perverted of minds.
